; --strict should report tag warnings at the item's line, not end of xact
account Assets:Cash
account Expenses:Food
commodity $

2012-03-22 Food
    ; :unknown_tag:
    Expenses:Food             $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --strict
             $-20.00  Assets:Cash
              $20.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
__ERROR__
Warning: "$FILE", line 6: Unknown metadata tag 'unknown_tag'
end test
